floxy
floxy

floxy is a simple service that permit end-to-end ultra secure connection between a remote and a host.
In few steps, click on the button generate new floxy, and our service will create a new one binary with
dual step async certificate and unique challenge to connect to our server. You just can download one time
each of one of binary remote and local. Now, just run:

whats the difference between floxy and other great services like ngrock, etc? Floxy don't expose the remote machine on internet,
only who has access to those binary can connect each other

great for developers that has needs to expose a service or preview a feature to other peer
great raspberry owners that want to connect to ssh port over the internet without exposing it